::Feline::
She could tell that He wasn't going to be easy to win, if at all.  
She purred slightly.  And walked away from him. She swayed her hips 
as she walked away from him. "OK then, we can pass the time in silnce 
if you like."  She sat down in the chair next to her console and 
crossed her legs. Her tail was laying over her lap and the end 
twitching.  She purred softly, in a low, steady purr.
